1. Under the **Settings** tab, click **Assign AZs and Networks** in the side panel.

1. Select the region under **Place singleton jobs in** and **Balance other jobs in**.

1. Select the **Network** to deploy to tile to.

1. Click **Save**

1. Click **Services Access** in the side panel.

1. Ensure **Enable global access to plans of service CredHub Service Broker** is checked.

1. Click **Save**

1. Click on **Errands** in the side panel.

1. Ensure **deploy-all** is set to **Default (On)** under **Post-Deploy Errands**.

1. Ensure **delete-all** is set to **Default (On)** under **Pre-Delete Errands**.

1. Click **Save**.

1. Return to the Ops Manager Installation Dashboard and click **Apply changes** to install YOUR-PRODUCT-NAME tile.

